      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <p>Modern science research requires massive amounts of computational
resources. Instruments produce data at the petabyte scale. In addition, modern
research teams are dynamic, constantly growing and changing to meet the needs
of the science discovery process. The shared processing power, storage,
instruments, software and networks a team assembles through its members will
change during the life of an experiment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <p>The VC3 project goal is to create the software to build and use
virtual clusters that represent these changing resources. With virtual
clusters, peers scattered all over the globe can use federated resources in a
way that is flexible and agile.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

